<span class="pl-s1">    <span class="pl-c1"><span class="pl-c1">padding</span></span>: <span class="pl-c1">0</span>;</span>
<span class="pl-s1">}</span>
<span class="pl-s1"></span><span class="pl-s1">&lt;</span>/<span class="pl-ent">style</span>&gt;
&lt;<span class="pl-ent">ul</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="pl-ent">li</span>&gt;first&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">li</span>&gt;
    &lt;<span class="pl-ent">li</span>&gt;second&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">li</span>&gt;
&lt;/<span class="pl-ent">ul</span>&gt;
&lt;<span class="pl-ent">script</span>&gt;<span class="pl-s1"></span>
<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c"><span class="pl-c">//</span> 脚本代码的第一级缩进与所属的 script 标签对齐</span></span>
<span class="pl-s1"><span class="pl-c1">require</span>([<span class="pl-s"><span class="pl-pds">'</span>app<span class="pl-pds">'</span></span>], <span class="pl-k">function</span> (<span class="pl-smi">app</span>) {</span>
<span class="pl-s1">    <span class="pl-smi">app</span>.<span class="pl-en">init</span>();</span>
<span class="pl-s1">});</span>
<span class="pl-s1"></span><span class="pl-s1">&lt;</span>/<span class="pl-ent">script</span>&gt;</pre></div>
        <h4><a href="#建议-每行不得超过-120-个字符" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-建议-每行不得超过-120-个字符"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[建议] 每行不得超过 <code>120</code> 个字符。</h4>
        <p>解释：</p>
        <p>过长的代码不容易阅读与维护。但是考虑到 HTML 的特殊性，不做硬性要求。</p>
        <h3><a href="#22-命名" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-22-命名"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>2.2 命名</h3>
        <h4><a href="#强制-class-必须单词全字母小写单词间以---分隔" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-class-必须单词全字母小写单词间以---分隔"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] <code>class</code> 必须单词全字母小写，单词间以 <code>-</code> 分隔。</h4>
        <h4><a href="#强制-class-必须代表相应模块或部件的内容或功能不得以样式信息进行命名" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-强制-class-必须代表相应模块或部件的内容或功能不得以样式信息进行命名"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[强制] <code>class</code> 必须代表相应模块或部件的内容或功能，不得以样式信息进行命名。</h4>
