        <p><code>src</code> 取值为空，会导致部分浏览器重新加载一次当前页面，参考：<a href="https://developer.yahoo.com/performance/rules.html#emptysrc" rel="nofollow">https://developer.yahoo.com/performance/rules.html#emptysrc</a></p>
        <h4><a href="#建议-避免为-img-添加不必要的-title-属性" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor" id="user-content-建议-避免为-img-添加不必要的-title-属性"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="octicon octicon-link" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>[建议] 避免为 <code>img</code> 添加不必要的 <code>title</code> 属性。</h4>
